<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Denzel Marani - Photography Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 50%, #7e22ce 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) inset;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        header {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            position: relative;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 4em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #7e22ce 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            color: #7e22ce;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 120px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3c72, #7e22ce);
            margin: 25px auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
            animation: expandWidth 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }

        @keyframes expandWidth {
            from {
                width: 0;
            }
            to {
                width: 120px;
            }
        }

        .intro-section {
            margin: 50px 0;
            text-align: left;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.8s both;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .intro-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #7e22ce 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .intro-section p {
            font-size: 1.15em;
            color: #34495e;
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #7e22ce 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .gallery-preview {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #7e22ce 100%);
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .gallery-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover::before {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #7e22ce 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 15px 10px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-button::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover::before {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.4);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 2px solid rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.1);
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                letter-spacing: -1px;
            }

            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }

            .intro-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.6em;
            }

            .intro-section p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .gallery-preview {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 15px;
            }

            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 15px 0;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Denzel Marani</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Photography & Visual Arts</p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </header>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Welcome</h2>
            <p>
                Hi! I'm <span class="highlight">Denzel Marani</span>, a passionate photographer dedicated to capturing moments that tell stories. 
                With a keen eye for detail and a love for visual storytelling, I specialize in creating compelling imagery across various genres.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>About My Work</h2>
            <p>
                My portfolio showcases a diverse range of photography projects. From stunning landscapes to intimate portraits, 
                each image is crafted with intention and care. I believe in the power of photography to <span class="highlight">inspire, 
                connect, and preserve</span> meaningful moments.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Portfolio Categories</h2>
            <div class="gallery-preview">
                <div class="gallery-item">Portraits</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Landscapes</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Events</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Lifestyle</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Travel</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Nature</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                Interested in commissioning a photo session or learning more about my work? 
                I'd love to hear from you!
            </p>
            <div class="cta-section">
                <button class="cta-button">View Full Portfolio</button>
                <button class="cta-button">Get in Touch</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Denzel Marani Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
